|image=[[Image:TraDec 15V.jpg|150px|Gaius Messius Quintus Traianus Decius]]
|caption=Coin of Decius, Roman Emperor defeated and killed in the battle
|date=Summer (July or August), [[251]]
|place=[[Moesia Inferior]] (modern [[Razgrad]], {{BUL}})
