* [[Joannes Zonaras|Zonaras]], ''Epitome historiarum'' ({{lang-el|Επιτομή ιστοριών}}), book 12, in ''[[Patrologia Graeca]]'', ed. [[J. P. Migne]], Paris, 1864, vol 134
* [[Zosimus]], ''Historia Nova'' ({{lang-el|Νέα Ιστορία}}), book 1, in ''Corpus Scriptorum Historiae Byzantinae'', ed. Bekker, Weber, Bonn, 1837
&lt;/div&gt;

