    <title>Battle of El Alamein</title>
    <id>4987</id>
    <revision>
      <id>391856972</id>
      <timestamp>2010-10-20T15:52:49Z</timestamp>
      <contributor>
        <username>Nnh</username>
        <id>21524</id>
      </contributor>
      <minor />
      <comment>+ja:</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">There were two '''battles of [[El Alamein]]''' in [[World War II]], both fought in 1942. The Battles occurred in [[Egypt]] in and around an area named after a railway stop called [[El Alamein]] at {{coord|30|49|20.89|N|28|57|15.51|E|type:event|display=inline,title}}.

* [[First Battle of El Alamein]] – 1–27 July 1942
* [[Second Battle of El Alamein]] – 23 October – 4 November 1942

