      <comment>/* Motor Racing Developments */ Rm all caps from ref title</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{for|people with the surname Brabham|Brabham (surname)}}
{{for|the place in Australia called Brabham|Brabham, Western Australia}}
{{Featured article}}
{{Former F1 team |
 Short_name = Brabham |
 Long_name = {{Flag icon|UK}} Motor Racing Developments, Ltd.|
 Logo = [[File:Brabham91.png]] |
