|conflict=Battle of Actium
|partof=The [[Final War of the Roman Republic]]
|image=[[File:Castro Battle of Actium.jpg|300px|''The Battle of Actium'', by Lorenzo A. Castro, painted 1672.]]
|caption=Baroque painting of the battle of Actium by Lorenzo A. Castro, 1672
