  | publisher = News Limited
  | date = 6 February 2008
  | url = http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/sport/the-bondi-betrayal/story-e6frexni-1111115483305
  | accessdate = 18 February 2010}}&lt;/ref&gt; A Broncos supporters group called &quot;The Thoroughbreds&quot; which is made up of prominent businessmen, made an unsuccessful bid to purchase News Ltd's controlling share of the club in 2007.&lt;ref&gt;{{cite news
