      <comment>/* Success in the 1950s and 1960s */</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the singer|the album|Bo Diddley (album)|the song|Bo Diddley (song)}}
{{Infobox musical artist
|Name                =Bo Diddley
|Img                 =Bo Diddley Prag 2005 02.jpg
|Background          =solo_singer
|Birth_name          =Ellas Otha Bates
|Alias               =Ellas McDaniel
