===Relay (4&amp;times;6 km)===
The women's relay event has been competed over three different distances:
* 3&amp;times;7.5&amp;nbsp;km &amp;mdash; 1992
* 4&amp;times;7.5&amp;nbsp;km &amp;mdash; 1994–2002
* 4&amp;times;6&amp;nbsp;km &amp;mdash; 2006-2010

