*[[Biathlon World Championships 1962|1962]] {{flagicon|Finland}} [[Hämeenlinna]], [[Finland]]
*[[Biathlon World Championships 1963|1963]] {{flagicon|Austria}} [[Seefeld, Tirol|Seefeld]], [[Austria]]
*[[Biathlon World Championships 1965|1965]] {{flagicon|Norway}} [[Elverum]], [[Norway]]
