=== Relay (4 x 6 km) ===
This event was first held in 1984. Through 1988, the event was 3 x 5&amp;nbsp;km. 1989-91: 3 x 7.5&amp;nbsp;km. 1993-2001: 4 x 7.5&amp;nbsp;km. In 2003, the leg distance was set to 6&amp;nbsp;km.

