==Mixed==
===Relay===
This event was first held in 2005, at the [[Biathlon World Cup]] finals in [[Khanty-Mansiysk]]. In 2005 the women biathletes did the first two legs, and the men did the following two, while in 2006 the sequence was woman&amp;ndash;man&amp;ndash;woman&amp;ndash;man. At the [[Biathlon World Championships 2007]] in [[Rasen-Antholz|Antholz]], the sequence was women&amp;ndash;women&amp;ndash;man&amp;ndash;man. The men ski legs of 7.5&amp;nbsp;km (in 2005-06: 6&amp;nbsp;km) and the women ski 6&amp;nbsp;km each. From 2007 only one team per nation is allowed to compete.

